# Project documentation
# Basic:
#   - Project: Vite React currency changer
#   - Purpose: convert currencies in a React app
#   - Structure: src/, public/, package.json, vite.config.js
# Advanced:
#   - Uses React hooks for state and effect management
#   - API integration for exchange rates or local sample data
#   - Includes error handling, loading states, and modular components
#   - Build output is stored in dist/ and ignored from version control
